"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Unrest happened outside a hospital where a man suspected of killing a five-year-old girl was being treated.\",            \"english_title\": \"Hospital Unrest\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hubo problemas afuera de un hospital donde un hombre sospechoso de matar a una ni\u00f1a de cinco a\u00f1os estaba siendo tratado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Problemas en el Hospital\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Nobel Peace Prize winner has been in jail since she was removed from power in a military coup in 2021.\",            \"english_title\": \"Nobel Winner in Jail\",            \"translated_version\": \"La ganadora del Premio Nobel de la Paz est\u00e1 en la c\u00e1rcel desde que fue sacada del poder en un golpe militar en 2021.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ganadora del Nobel en la C\u00e1rcel\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US Central Command has a plan for quick and strong strikes on Iran, according to Axios.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Plan on Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Comando Central de EE.UU. tiene un plan para ataques r\u00e1pidos y fuertes en Ir\u00e1n, seg\u00fan Axios.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Plan de EE.UU. para Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least nine people, including two children, were killed, says Lebanon's health ministry.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tragedy in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos nueve personas, incluyendo dos ni\u00f1os, murieron, dice el ministerio de salud de L\u00edbano.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tragedia en L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Pro-Palestinian activists say 22 boats carrying aid for Gaza were stopped illegally in international waters near the Greek island.\",            \"english_title\": \"Aid Boats Stopped\",            \"tr